It is also revealed that she is Fran's sister, along with Mjrn.

===Jules===
'''Jules''' is a streetear in Archades who knows the value of knowledge and teaches Vaan the ways of surviving in Archadia. Also an old friend of Balthier, though the sky pirate does not acknowledge it as so.

===King Raminas B'nargin Dalmasca===
{| class="wikitable"
