'''Raminas B'nargin Dalmasca''' is the father of Ashe and eight deceased princes who ruled Dalmasca before its invasion. After Dalmasca's fall to the Archadian Empire, he was forced to acknowledge a "peace treaty" - the sign to approve Archadia's occupation and Dalmasca's surrender - but Vayne had Judge Gabranth murder him while pretending to be Basch soon after.

